WEBVTT

00:00:10.948 --> 00:00:19.832 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
God has brought us into his fold.
We enjoy the things he foretold.

00:00:19.832 --> 00:00:28.465 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Unity and peace we possess,
Bringing such happiness.

00:00:28.465 --> 00:00:37.433 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Unity we cherish;
Harmony is sweet.

00:00:37.433 --> 00:00:46.984 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In God’s work there’s much to be done.
He directs us now through his Son.

00:00:46.984 --> 00:00:56.243 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
May we serve obediently,
Working in harmony.

00:01:02.708 --> 00:01:11.634 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As we pray for oneness of mind
And we all take care to be kind,

00:01:11.634 --> 00:01:20.184 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Love will grow and praise will increase,
Giving us joy and peace.

00:01:20.184 --> 00:01:29.234 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Peace is so refreshing,
Bringing such delight.

00:01:29.234 --> 00:01:38.535 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As we show true brotherly love,
God will grant us peace from above.

00:01:38.535 --> 00:01:49.588 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With his help, united we’ll be,
Serving him endlessly.

